728837f-a.title: Richmond: Forest Avenue - Ordell Avenue
728837f-a.text:
1281 and 1273 Forest Avenue, north side, at the head of Ordell
Avenue. No. 1281 is the M. W. Wheeler house (1874 map). It was
earlier (1853 map) the Houseman house.
May 4, 1932.
P. L. Sperr,
